                  <summary>Miracles of Mary</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="2r" to="31v" facs="002"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT2384Taamme"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><title type="complete" ref="LIT2384Taamme"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Introduction to the Miracles of Mary </note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><title type="complete" ref="LIT2384Taamme"/>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Thirty-Eight Miracles of Mary, including, for instance (the miracles are unnumbered; many folios are covered with paintings)</note>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.1"><locus from="5V" to="6R" facs="006"/><title>The woman from Cairo who lived by the river and whose daughter became blind</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀለወት እሐቲ ብእሲት ምስለ ሐማታ በይወለ ቃትራ ወቢታኒ በጽንፈ ባሕር ወመዋግዲሁ ይበጽሕ ውስተ</incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.2"><locus from="6r" to="6v" facs="006"/><title>The daughter of the rich man from Caesarea who could not deliver her baby</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀለወት አሐቲ ብእሲት እምዓበይተ ሀገር ዘቂሳርያ ወኮነ አቡሃባዕለ በሕቁ በወርቅ ወበብሩር</incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.3"><locus from="6v" to="7r" facs="007"/><title>The faded icon of Saint Mary that the mother-in-law wanted to discard</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀለወት አሐቲ ብእሲት ምስለ ሐማታ ዘታፈቅራ ለእግዝእትነ ቅድስት ድንግል በ፪ማርያም ወላዲተ መለኮት ወሶበ</incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.4"><locus from="7r" to="7v" facs="007"/><title>The sinful deacon who was healed by a drop of Saint Mary's milk</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀሎ ፩መስፍን ሐራዊ ዘንጉሥ ውስተ ጠርሲስ ዘዊልቅያ ወዲይቆን ውእቱ ዘበስም</incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.5"><locus from="7v" to="8r" facs="008"/><title>The woman from Cairo whose children all died</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀለወት አሐቲ ብእሲት በዳወ ቃሐራ ወወለደተ ፯ውሉደ ወሞቱ ኵሎሙ</incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.6"><locus from="8r" to="8v" facs="008"/><title>Mareqos, King of Romeya, abandons his throne secretly to become a monk</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">: ወሀሎ ፩ብአሲ ዘስሙ ማርቆስ ንጉሠ ሮምያ እምድኅረ አቡሁ ንጉሥ ዘስሙ ገብራ ኢያሱስ</incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.7"><locus from="8v" to="9r" facs="009"/><title>The thief whom the king's soldiers could not kill(?)</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀሎ ፩ ብእሲ በሀገረ ገላትያ ዘስሙ ቂራስ ሠራዊ ውእቱ ወፈያታዊ ወቀታሌ ነፍስ</incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.8"><locus from="9r" to="9v" facs="009"/><title>Saint Mary commands a deacon to give Christian burial to a sinful deacon assassinated by his enemies; when they disinter him, a flower is found in his mouth</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀሎ ፩ዲያቆን ውስተ አሐቲ ደሴት ዘባሕረ ኢያሪኮ አንተ ስማ ገሪሳት ውእቱሰ ዲያቆን ዘማዊ ውእቱ ወይገብር</incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.9"><locus from="9v" to="10r" facs="010"/><title>Covered with paintings</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.10"><locus from="10v" to="11r" facs="011"/><title>The pious monk scribe who used to write Saint Mary's name in golden ink</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀሎ ፩ መነከስ ዘይነብር በሀገረ ፊልጵስዩስ ዘስሙ ድምያኖስ ለእግዝአትነ ቅድስት ድንግል ብ፪ማርያም ወላዲተ መለኮት እማእምቀ ልቡ<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.11"><locus from="11v" to="12r" facs="012"/><title>The monk, Yǝsḥaq, who prayed for seven years that Saint Mary would appear to him</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀሎ ፩ መነኮስ ኄር ዘስሙ ይስሐቅ ወያፈቅራ ለእግዝእትነ ቅድስት ድንግል<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.12"><locus from="12r" to="12v" facs="012"/><title>Maryam from Dǝfrā, a child who wanted to receive Communion but was shut up in the house when her family went to church</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀሎ ፩ ብእሲ ፈራሄ እግዚአብሔር ዘይፈቅራ ለእግዝአትነ ቅድስት ድንግል <gap reason="omitted"/> ሀገሩሰ ድፍራ ወአውሰበ ብእሲተ</incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.13"><locus from="12v" to="13r" facs="013"/><title>The French artist who fell from the scaffolding while painting frescoes</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀሎ ፩ ብእሲ ሰዓሊ ወአልቦ ዘይትማሰሎ በውእቱ አዝማን በገብረ ሥዕል</incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.14"><locus from="13r" to="13v" facs="013"/><title>Saint Mary carries a dying monk to Jerusalem</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀለወት ሥዕለ እግዝእትነ ቅድስት ድንግል በ፪ማርያም ወላዲተ አምላክ በደብረ ነጋድያን በቤተ ሕሙማን መንገለ</incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.15"><locus from="13v" to="14v" facs="014"/><title>The young man who used to bring roses to the icon of Saint Mary</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀሎ ፩ወሬዛ ዘሠናይ አርአያሁ ዘስሙ ዘካርያስ እምዘመደ መንግሥት ዘሀግረ ሮሜ</incipit>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.16"><locus from="14v" facs="015"/><title>The two women who were attacked by robbers on their way to church</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወሀለዋ ክልኤ አንስት አእማተ እግዝእትነ ቅድስት ድንግል በ፪ማርያም ወላዲተ ፈጠሪ በቤተ ልሔም እምአዋልደ ይሁዳ ስማ ለአሐቲ ዮልያና</incipit>
                </msItem>
              </msItem>
            </msItem>
